profile: Hi, my name is Max Leblanc and I live in Memramcook NB. I started my business in January 2021. I clean Mini-Splits, Ductwork and Dryer Vents. We travel to the Greater Moncton area, Shediac, Cap-pele, Bouctouche, Rexton, Richibuctou, Salisbury, AuLac, Sackville, Petitcodiac, Hillsborough. Please call for your free estimate. I look forward to hearing from you!
